Intro
=====
Bootstrap Ruby on Rails Application with following gems and pre-configuration:
- Authlogic
- Can Can
- High Voltage
- a contact form.
- paperclip
- Unicorn for server

It's a perfect start for presentation/portfolio/blog/website. It should also be preconfigured to be deployed in Heroku

testing
--------
- cucumber
- rspec
- capybara
- shoulda
- Factory girl



HOW TO:
=======
Changes to be done before starting:
- replace all occurences of the application name "Loicginoux" by your app name.
- mail configuration in the initializer needs to be adjust for each app
- production.rb: change asset host
- development.rb: change asset host

and then run in your development environment:
```
foreman start
```
it should be running in 0.0.0.0:5000


